                        <interp inst="t18360704-name-166" type="surname" value="BROOK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360704-name-166" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>DAVID BROOK</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Diamond-row, Stepeny-green. I was coming</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183607040020"></xptr>
               <p>down the Minories, and saw the prisoner and another young man looking in at the shop window—I saw the prisoner take the brass from the window—I went in, and informed Devereux—we pursued the prisoner, and saw him drop the brass in George-street, and pursued him till we gave him in charge.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I never had it—the man who took it was let go.</p>
